&lt;p data-start=&quot;1004&quot; data-end=&quot;1280&quot;&gt;You are highly organised, deeply connected, commercially sharp, and impossible to rattle. Whether negotiating supplier agreements, managing shifting production realities, or leading a high-pressure set, you bring confidence, clarity, and control to every stage of the process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1282&quot; data-end=&quot;1414&quot;&gt;Most importantly, you care about the standard. The details. The craft. The feeling people are left with after seeing the final work.&lt;/p&gt;
