&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3wncd3&quot; data-start=&quot;1616&quot; data-end=&quot;1780&quot;&gt;Own the operational and financial health of assigned projects from initial scoping through final delivery, balancing creative ambition with commercial discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
